&lt;p&gt;Brasserie &lt;em&gt;Gastronom&lt;/em&gt; is a case where two recognized experts in their field: the businessman-restaurateur Kirill Gusev and brilliant Russian chef Anatoly Komm partnered&nbsp;to create a restaurant where you can get daily gastronomic pleasures at the very affordable prices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The interior of Gastronom was created by designer Elena Turina, who was inspired by the elements used in expensive hotels and apartments in the south climate. Thanks to the huge panoramic windows overlooking Moscow, there is a lot of light&nbsp;that abounds. Through the use of high-quality natural materials, the space is quite reserved about colours, but very cozy and comfortable, the main message throughout the&nbsp;restaurant.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Of course, the essence of the restaurant is gastronomy! The chef, like a fashion designer, has created a menu featuring a collection of flavors and dishes, sampled&nbsp;in different parts of the world, and presented in the author&amp;#8217;s presentation of Anatoly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gastronom is the perfect place for daily visits, whether its a business meeting, a date with a loved one or a meeting of good friends!&lt;/p&gt;
